    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its eight individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains sharp with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates, while the suspension geometry ensures neutral handling and communicative steering feedback. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly and induction system are track-ready. A mechanically robust specimen for the discerning driver.",
